{"tid":991863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沿用 38 年後終升級　MIDI 2.0 計劃始動！","createTime":"2019-01-22T16:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T18:12:06.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"23b8a746bc418845bd2bde24a932fb687f8c065c","tid":991863,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/01/21/沿用38年後終升級-midi-2計劃始動/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2019%2F01%2F21%2F%E6%B2%BF%E7%94%A838%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E7%B5%82%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-midi-2%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%A7%8B%E5%8B%95%2F&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f33de133\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/01/21/沿用38年後終升級-midi-2計劃始動/</a><br />\n<br />\n自小玩電腦遊戲和電腦模擬電子琴，相信都會留意到 MIDI 這個名詞。可能會有人以為它是電子音樂的格式，但其實 MIDI 是電子樂器間通信的通信協定，讓樂器與電腦以至舞台演出裝置可以彼此連接、同步和即時交換演奏資料。經過 38 年歲月，這個通信協定終於要升級了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/l_koya_dx7-710x302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fl_koya_dx7-710x302.jpg&h=b85ced8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n透過 MIDI 介面，即使是 1983 年 MIDI 協定制訂時所推出的電子琴，一樣可以與最新的 iPhone 連接。<br />\n<br />\n米國 The MIDI Manufacturers Association (MMA) 和日本音樂電子協會（ AMEI ）周末宣布共同制訂 MIDI 2.0 新一代電子樂器界面協定，並計於 2019 年 1 月 24 -27 日舉行的冬季 NAMM Show 中進行僅供會員企業參加的互通性插拔大會（ Plugfest ），而參與的公司就包括 Ableton/Cycling &rsquo;74 、 Art+Logic 、 Bome Software 、 imitone 、 Native Instruments 、 Roland 、 ROLI 、Steinberg 、 TouchKeys 和 Yamaha。另外，積極開發在瀏覽器播放 MIDI 音樂的 Web MIDI API 的 Google 也會參加。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-8-710x603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F03-8-710x603.jpg&h=4b501546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMIDI 2.0 環境<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/01/20/midi20/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F01%2F20%2Fmidi20%2Flife-tech%2F&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a53f76ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/01/20/midi20/life-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\nMIDI 2.0 草案正式發佈<br />\n<br />\n負責傳送、控制電子樂器的演奏數據的 MIDI 規格，將會帶來 38 年以來的全新版本。日本音樂電子事業協會與美國 MIDI Manufacturers Association 發表了「MIDI 2.0」格式，讓廠商能夠依此規格開發新一代電子樂器產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/20190119-00000032-it_nlab-000-1-view.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F20190119-00000032-it_nlab-000-1-view.jpg&h=980efcf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/螢幕截圖-2019-01-20-下午5.42.58-694x390.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-01-20-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.42.58-694x390.png&h=5bb9c3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMIDI 2.0 由美、日、全球多家業界大廠共同製定，原型開發者有 Crimson Technology、KORG、Roland、Yamaha、Zoom、Ableton/Cycling&lsquo;74、Art+Logic、Bome Software、Google、imitone、Native Instruments、ROLI、Steinberg、TouchKeys 等等。<br />\n<br />\nMIDI 2.0 能夠與 1.0 硬件作出兼容，而大幅提升了連接性能，以 MIDI-CI 為核心，各裝置之間連接後可互相通知對方自己是甚麼裝置、具備甚麼功能，可操控、被操控哪些參數等。演奏訊息亦由以前的 7bit 提升到 16bit，Poly、Channel Pressure、滑音訊息、控制變化訊息更從 7 bit 提升到 256bit，通道數量從 16 提升至 256。以上的規格可把演奏的數據再現性、表現力大幅提升。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/l_koya_dx7-694x295.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fl_koya_dx7-694x295.jpg&h=19ca7ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 1 月 24 日美國加州將舉行世界最大級別的音樂會議「The 2019 NAMM Show」，屆時或可窺探 2.0 策定後的全新電子音樂硬件。"},{"pid":"49c6f7573a06963f1cd312d7c653262517bffd44","tid":991863,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698d759f9af91374f5af5ff62eab635580dcfa16","tid":991863,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:10:24.000Z","msg":"點解無中國份？廿一世紀唔係中國世紀？中國人唔玩樂器？中國無中樂？"},{"pid":"a4fcfe06b92672937c85fcd091ee82b4124467e1","tid":991863,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"前幾日仲諗緊MIDI都咁耐 會唔會有新技術？"},{"pid":"237343d813f1e5f5437b67f1546a78213bbe3a2a","tid":991863,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"btw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好事"},{"pid":"622088e88cc30d79743c01adb43c139eafb55f94","tid":991863,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"竟然無Apple份"},{"pid":"75d45fb0a6bd61e4b04e0da09710fb0aa86deb39","tid":991863,"uid":168331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T18:12:06.000Z","msg":"希望cmidi都有2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}